r our priorities so that we increase our levels of companionship even at the risk of reducing our income.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aEconomicsxMoral and ethical aspects. 0aEconomicsxSociological aspects. 0aHappinessxSocial aspects. 0aMoneyxMoral and ethical aspects. 0aQuality of life. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000z978311053801440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030019131840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300191318423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300191318/original  a978-3-11-053801-4  Yale University Press eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000b2000  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles